title: Michigan fan cries way into viral ether
text:
(WVUE) - Michigan State stunned Michigan on the last play of the game Saturday.
The game was seemingly over and the Wolverines just needed to get the punt away.
But the punter fumbled and the rest is history.
Scott Edwards caught the moment in the stands on camera. "Although I'm feeling hurt and a lil salty, I'm not nearly as bad as homeboy that was next to me in the stadium! Lol."
Michigan fan is sad. (Warning: The video contains some offensive language)
Although I'm feeling hurt and a lil salty, I'm not nearly as bad as... Michigan state fan (and Pittsburgh Steeler superstar Le'Veon bell) is happy.
WE ARE SPARTA pic.twitter.com/QifqlNbTum
